<div><div><h2>Market in consolidation mode ahead of next move up, says Ambareesh Baliga</h2></div><div>"moneycontrol newsthe indian market witnessed a rollercoaster ride in october and november where small and midcaps took a beating. moneycontrol s kshitij anand on the sidelines of the 2018 wealth creator awards spoke to independent market expert ambareesh baliga to find out whether investors should catch a falling knife.true to his reputation baliga stated that the destruction in the mid and smallcaps is behind us and at present the market is witnessing a consolidation "before the next move up".tune in to find out what the market expert revealed."</div></div>